{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Obsidian AI Mini Server",
    "description": "REST API for accessing an Obsidian vault. Supports reading, writing, listing files, and user management.",
    "version": "0.2.3"
  },
  "paths": {
    "/api/obsidian": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Obsidian Vault Tool",
        "description": "Access the Obsidian vault. The request body is a JSON object with a **kind** field that determines the operation and its parameters:\n\n- **get_vault_info** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"get_vault_info\"}` \u2014 Returns vault name, daily-notes folder, and user info.\n- **read_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"read_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"offset\":0,\"limit\":20000}` \u2014 Read file content. `limit: -1` for unlimited.\n- **write_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"write_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"text\":\"...\"}` \u2014 Overwrite file with text.\n- **append_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"append_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"text\":\"...\"}` \u2014 Append text to file.\n- **replace_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"replace_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"old_text\":\"...\",\"new_text\":\"...\",\"count\":1}` \u2014 Replace text. `count: -1` for all occurrences.\n- **move_file** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"move_file\",\"old_path\":\"...\",\"new_path\":\"...\",\"make_copy\":false}` \u2014 Move, copy, or delete a file. Set `new_path: \"\"` to delete.\n- **list_files** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"list_files\",\"path\":\"\",\"extensions\":[\".md\"],\"max_depth\":1,\"offset\":0,\"limit\":100,\"sort_by\":\"name\",\"sort_order\":\"asc\"}` \u2014 List files and folders. `max_depth: -1` or `limit: -1` for unlimited.\n- **list_users** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"list_users\"}` \u2014 List all users (admin only).\n- **upsert_user** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"upsert_user\",\"username\":\"...\",\"token\":null,\"access\":null,\"is_admin\":null,\"delete_user\":null}` \u2014 Create, update, or delete a user (admin only).",
        "operationId": "obsidian_api_obsidian_post",
        "security": [
          {
            "HTTPBearer": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "request",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Access the Obsidian vault. The request body is a JSON object with a **kind** field that determines the operation and its parameters:\n\n- **get_vault_info** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"get_vault_info\"}` \u2014 Returns vault name, daily-notes folder, and user info.\n- **read_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"read_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"offset\":0,\"limit\":20000}` \u2014 Read file content. `limit: -1` for unlimited.\n- **write_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"write_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"text\":\"...\"}` \u2014 Overwrite file with text.\n- **append_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"append_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"text\":\"...\"}` \u2014 Append text to file.\n- **replace_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"replace_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"old_text\":\"...\",\"new_text\":\"...\",\"count\":1}` \u2014 Replace text. `count: -1` for all occurrences.\n- **move_file** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"move_file\",\"old_path\":\"...\",\"new_path\":\"...\",\"make_copy\":false}` \u2014 Move, copy, or delete a file. Set `new_path: \"\"` to delete.\n- **list_files** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"list_files\",\"path\":\"\",\"extensions\":[\".md\"],\"max_depth\":1,\"offset\":0,\"limit\":100,\"sort_by\":\"name\",\"sort_order\":\"asc\"}` \u2014 List files and folders. `max_depth: -1` or `limit: -1` for unlimited.\n- **list_users** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"list_users\"}` \u2014 List all users (admin only).\n- **upsert_user** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"upsert_user\",\"username\":\"...\",\"token\":null,\"access\":null,\"is_admin\":null,\"delete_user\":null}` \u2014 Create, update, or delete a user (admin only).\n",
              "title": "Request"
            },
            "description": "Access the Obsidian vault. The request body is a JSON object with a **kind** field that determines the operation and its parameters:\n\n- **get_vault_info** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"get_vault_info\"}` \u2014 Returns vault name, daily-notes folder, and user info.\n- **read_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"read_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"offset\":0,\"limit\":20000}` \u2014 Read file content. `limit: -1` for unlimited.\n- **write_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"write_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"text\":\"...\"}` \u2014 Overwrite file with text.\n- **append_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"append_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"text\":\"...\"}` \u2014 Append text to file.\n- **replace_text** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"replace_text\",\"path\":\"...\",\"old_text\":\"...\",\"new_text\":\"...\",\"count\":1}` \u2014 Replace text. `count: -1` for all occurrences.\n- **move_file** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"move_file\",\"old_path\":\"...\",\"new_path\":\"...\",\"make_copy\":false}` \u2014 Move, copy, or delete a file. Set `new_path: \"\"` to delete.\n- **list_files** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"list_files\",\"path\":\"\",\"extensions\":[\".md\"],\"max_depth\":1,\"offset\":0,\"limit\":100,\"sort_by\":\"name\",\"sort_order\":\"asc\"}` \u2014 List files and folders. `max_depth: -1` or `limit: -1` for unlimited.\n- **list_users** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"list_users\"}` \u2014 List all users (admin only).\n- **upsert_user** \u2014 `{\"kind\":\"upsert_user\",\"username\":\"...\",\"token\":null,\"access\":null,\"is_admin\":null,\"delete_user\":null}` \u2014 Create, update, or delete a user (admin only).\n"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Success"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VaultInfo"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FileText"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FilesList"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SearchResults"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UsersList"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BatchResponse"
                    }
                  ],
                  "discriminator": {
                    "propertyName": "kind",
                    "mapping": {
                      "success": "#/components/schemas/Success",
                      "error": "#/components/schemas/Error",
                      "vault_info": "#/components/schemas/VaultInfo",
                      "file_text": "#/components/schemas/FileText",
                      "files_list": "#/components/schemas/FilesList",
                      "search_results": "#/components/schemas/SearchResults",
                      "users_list": "#/components/schemas/UsersList",
                      "batch_response": "#/components/schemas/BatchResponse"
                    }
                  },
                  "title": "Response Obsidian Api Obsidian Post"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
